{"word":"Ἀγρίππας","slug":"Ἀγρίππας","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>Ἀγρίππας, α, ὁ</el></b> [Roman cognomen] <b><i>Agrippa,</i></b> Herod Agrippa II, son of Herod Agrippa I (simply mentioned as Herod <a href='B:510 12:1'>Ac 12</a>, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ s.\">s.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:Ἡρῴδης\">Ἡρῴδης</a></el> 3) and brother of Bernice <b><a href='B:510 25:1'>Ac 25</a></b> and<b> 26</b> passim. <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἄγριος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀγρός\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}